# CSS Grid ğŸ•¸ï¸

Designed for 2D layouts (rows AND columns).

```css
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 100px 200px auto;
  gap: 10px;
}
```

- `grid-template-columns`: Defines width of columns
- `fr`: Fractional unit (e.g., `1fr 1fr` = two equal columns)

## Grid Areas

```css
.header { grid-area: head; }
.menu { grid-area: menu; }
.container {
  grid-template-areas:
    'head head'
    'menu main';
}
```
